{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "程繁問於子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "程繁問於子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "7.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "「夫子曰『聖王不爲樂』，昔諸侯倦於聽治，息於鐘鼓之樂；", "text_normalized": "「夫子曰『聖王不爲樂』，昔諸侯倦於聽治，息於鐘鼓之樂；", "canonical_ref": "7.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "士大夫倦於聽治，息於竽瑟之樂；", "text_normalized": "士大夫倦於聽治，息於竽瑟之樂；", "canonical_ref": "7.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "農夫春耕夏耘，秋斂冬藏，息於聆缶之樂。", "text_normalized": "農夫春耕夏耘，秋斂冬藏，息於聆缶之樂。", "canonical_ref": "7.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "今夫子曰『聖王不爲樂』，此譬之猶馬駕而不稅，弓張而不弛，無乃非有血氣者之所能至邪？", "text_normalized": "今夫子曰『聖王不爲樂』，此譬之猶馬駕而不稅，弓張而不弛，無乃非有血氣者之所能至邪？", "canonical_ref": "7.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "」", "text_normalized": "」", "canonical_ref": "7.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "7.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "「昔者堯舜有茅茨者，且以爲禮，且以爲樂。", "text_normalized": "「昔者堯舜有茅茨者，且以爲禮，且以爲樂。", "canonical_ref": "7.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "湯放桀於大水，環天下自立以爲王，事成功立，無大後患，因先王之樂，又自作樂，命曰《護》，又修《九招》。", "text_normalized": "湯放桀於大水，環天下自立以爲王，事成功立，無大後患，因先王之樂，又自作樂，命曰《護》，又修《九招》。", "canonical_ref": "7.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "武王勝殷殺紂，環天下自立以爲王，事成功立，無大後患，因先王之樂，又自作樂，命曰《象》。", "text_normalized": "武王勝殷殺紂，環天下自立以爲王，事成功立，無大後患，因先王之樂，又自作樂，命曰《象》。", "canonical_ref": "7.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "周成王因先王之樂，又自作樂，命曰《騶虞》。", "text_normalized": "周成王因先王之樂，又自作樂，命曰《騶虞》。", "canonical_ref": "7.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "周成王之治天下也，不若武王。", "text_normalized": "周成王之治天下也，不若武王。", "canonical_ref": "7.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "武王之治天下也，不若成湯。", "text_normalized": "武王之治天下也，不若成湯。", "canonical_ref": "7.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "成湯之治天下也，不若堯舜。", "text_normalized": "成湯之治天下也，不若堯舜。", "canonical_ref": "7.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "故其樂逾繁者，其治逾寡。", "text_normalized": "故其樂逾繁者，其治逾寡。", "canonical_ref": "7.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "自此觀之，樂非所以治天下也。", "text_normalized": "自此觀之，樂非所以治天下也。", "canonical_ref": "7.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "」", "text_normalized": "」", "canonical_ref": "7.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "程繁曰：", "text_normalized": "程繁曰：", "canonical_ref": "7.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "「子曰『聖王無樂』，此亦樂已，若之何其謂聖王無樂也？", "text_normalized": "「子曰『聖王無樂』，此亦樂已，若之何其謂聖王無樂也？", "canonical_ref": "7.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "」", "text_normalized": "」", "canonical_ref": "7.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "7.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "「聖王之命也，多寡之。", "text_normalized": "「聖王之命也，多寡之。", "canonical_ref": "7.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "食之利也，以知饑而食之者智也，因爲無智矣。", "text_normalized": "食之利也，以知饑而食之者智也，因爲無智矣。", "canonical_ref": "7.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "今聖有樂而少，此亦無也。", "text_normalized": "今聖有樂而少，此亦無也。", "canonical_ref": "7.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument", "source_id": "mozi-007-threefold-argument__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "」", "text_normalized": "」", "canonical_ref": "7.25", "notes": ""}
